  "body": "### Description\nAs a Besu Dev, I want to understand the interaction between ipv6 and peering so that we can make recommendations to users. \n\n### Acceptance Criteria\nDoes enabling ipv6 (eg on docker config) improve the quality of peers? \nIs this different for different testnets? Mainnet?\nIf so, we should make recommend for users to enable ipv6 as appropriate (either by updating the docs or docker images)\n\n\n",
